  "lyrics": {
    "v1": "God the Father, be our Stay, When hell&#39;s dread pow&#39;rs assail us; Cleanse us from our sins, we pray, Nor in our last hour fail us. Keep us from the Evil One; Firm in the faith abiding, In Christ our Savior hiding, And hearti- ly confiding. Let us put God&#39;s armor on: With all true Christians running Our heav&#39;nly race and shunning The devil&#39;s wiles and cunning. Amen, Amen, this be done, So sing we, Hallelujah!",
    "v2": "Jesus Christ be Thou our Stay, Cleanse us from our sins, we pray, Nor in our last hour fail us. Keep us from the Evil One; Firm in the faith abiding, In Christ our Savior hiding, And hearti- ly confiding. Let us put God&#39;s armor on: With all true Christians running Our heav&#39;nly race and shunning The devil&#39;s wiles and cunning. Amen, Amen, this be done, So sing we, Hallelujah!",
    "v3": "Holy Ghost, be Thou our Stay, Cleanse us from our sins, we pray, Nor in our last hour fail us. Keep us from the Evil One; Firm in the faith abiding, In Christ our Savior hiding, And hearti- ly confiding. Let us put God&#39;s armor on: With all true Christians running Our heav&#39;nly race and shunning The devil&#39;s wiles and cunning. Amen, Amen, this be done, So sing we, Hallelujah!",
    "v4": "1(alt). Triune God, be Thou our Stay, Cleanse us from our sins, we pray, Nor in our last hour fail us. Keep us from the Evil One; Firm in the faith abiding, In Christ our Savior hiding, And hearti- ly confiding. Let us put God&#39;s armor on: With all true Christians running Our heav&#39;nly race and shunning The devil&#39;s wiles and cunning. Amen, Amen, this be done, So sing we, Hallelujah!"
  },
